.SH Description
.PP
\f[C]MPI_Comm_create_errhandler\f[] creates an error handler that can be
attached to communicators.
This \f[C]function\f[] is identical to \f[C]MPI_Errhandler_create\f[],
the use of which is deprecated.
In C, the user routine should be a \f[C]function\f[] of type
\f[C]MPI_Comm_errhandler_function\f[], which is defined as
.IP
.nf
